        <h1>About Aashroy</h1><hr>
    </div>

    <p class="p-5 lead text-left">Aashroy is working for the benefit of the homeless and deprived sections of the society, 
      especially poor people of the Society. We take up and execute projects to promote welfare of the 
      community they work with. They work to address various concerns and issues prevailing within the society.
       NGOs are not-for-profit bodies which means they do not have any commercial interest. To alleviate their 
       suffering and bring dignity to these people 
      we are bringing up a concept name Aashroy which will provide shelter,food, medical care clothing and all 
      the necessities for obtaining a comfortable life.This organizations fight for uplifting women, children,
      and every other person who is suffering in any form. Moreover, the main motive of these associations is to
      establish a flourishing society with no odds and uncertainties and when their times of downhearted, 
      they get back their smile and cherry moments back. We as a team will consist of people with different motives for working. The most important are desire to achieve
      a social mission; professional self-realization, eg acquisition of new skills, knowledge and experience; and the desire to work in a team in a pleasant environment.
     </p>
     <div class="text-black" style="padding: 0px 15%; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">
      <p class="px-2" style="background-color: rgba(3, 134, 9, 0.37) ; "><b> Our team recognize that all people are born free and equal in dignity and we are sensitive to the moral values, religion, customs, 
        traditions, and culture of the communities they serve. And we respect the integrity of families and support family-based life and also respect religious freedom.</b> </p>
     </div>
      

      



