          <h2><b> We Organise Health Camps</b><span class="text-muted"> in Remote places </span></h2>
          <p>In addition to taking care of the physical health by having Doctors, Nurses, and Ayas to support thousands of human beings
            within our premises, we also take care of mental health needs such as counselling, outdoor activities, keeping the environment
            clean with greenery and so on thereby resulting in upbeat perspective of life for everyone.
            
            A Free medical Camp can be considered as a life-saving program that aims to provide free medical and 
            surgical services to poor communities living in rural or urban areas by a mobile team with varieties of medical specialized services. 
            <div style="line-height: 2;">
              -Provide free and high-quality medical services and full body complete medical checkup for the poor population. <br>
            
              -Working as an emergency team in disasters. <br>
              
              -Raise health awareness among the community and teach them to deal with communicable and no communicable. <br>
              
              -Register rare and severe cases and refer them to specialized centers. <br>
              
              -Evaluate the living conditions and determine the obstacles and challenges to work on solving their problems.</p>
